snippet.title: Mini Miners Trailer Official
snippet.description:
Mini Miners is a resource management strategy game available for BNB Chain, brought to you by Seascape Network. Hire and manage miners to collect resources that can be used to improve their efficiency and grow your mining empire. Find the best path forward to maximize your output by carefully acquiring and utilizing resources, trading on the open market, and sharing with your friends. A little goes a long way! 

To the Mines
